These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, sprite, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person drinking water is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | juice | sprite | hot-chocolate | water   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, avocado, cranberry, pear
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating avocado##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Food   | cranberry    | avocado      | eggplant | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, tennis, weightlifting, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | weightlifting   | tennis |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, mauve, purple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | purple | grey | lilac  | mauve      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, filmmaking, cooking
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | filmmaking | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, begonia, amaryllis
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | begonia | marigold | rose |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

