.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie, salsa
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, ivory, apricot
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Color           | ivory | blood-red | apricot       | mauve |

