2. the person who growslily is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Flower   | balloon-flower          | sunflower | zinnia     | lily    |

