.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, scrabble, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, train, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Game    | billiard | scrabble  | mah-jongg | backgammon |
| Transport   | tram | train | taxi          | bus    |

