.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, domino, billiard
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Game   | monopoly  | domino | billiard           | whist   |

