.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, surfing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Sport     | surfing  | baseball    | parkour       | ice-hockey |

 